metadata.title: Every Step You Take Blue Heeler Is Always Watching You T-Shirt
features: Solid colors: 100% Cotton; Heather Grey: 90% Cotton, 10% Polyester; All Other Heathers: 50% Cotton, 50% Polyester
The trait of a Heeler, no matter Blue, Red or Cattledog, they will be watching you
This is a great gift for any occasion. Birthday, Valentine's Day, put it in a Easter Basket or Christmas Stocking, or just to say I Love You
Lightweight, Classic fit, Double-needle sleeve and bottom hem
description: So many different names for a Blue Heeler, No matter what you call them, they will protect you and love you more then you will ever know. Australian Cattle Dog, Queensland Heeler, Cattledog, Red Heeler, Blue Heeler and I am sure more. Cattledogs are a special breed, so this would perfect for yourself or as a gift. Do you know someone who loves their Heeler? Gift them this great item.
